.desktop files in {{Path|/usr/share/applications/}} should not be executable

But on 2017-06-16 many ebuilds create executable .desktop files. {{Bug|621966}}
This page intends to collect information about common problems and how to fix these.

===Find problematic packages/files ===

Look for executable .desktop files on your system with
{{Cmd|find /usr/share/applications/ -executable -type f}}

Please report upstream, if necessary.

